%C A083219 a(n) is n+2 with its second least significant bit removed (see A021913(n+2) for that bit). - _Kevin Ryde_, Dec 13 2019
%H A083219 Altug Alkan, <a href="/A083219/b083219.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..10000</a>
